race.comment: THINK OF ONE (7) broke through for his maiden win over 1815m at Port Macquarie last time, scoring comfortably. Shaping up nicely and gets the key booking of Bullock. Can go right on with it now. THE AMBASSADOR (9) finished fifth last time out over 1600m at Coffs Harbour three weeks ago. Will appreciate the rise in journey and is drawn perfectly. Can give this a big shake. BONFIDELITY (8) finished fourth two runs back then improved last start but found a couple better at Inverell. Rises sharply in trip third-up and gets her chance to break a long run of outs. FIREALARM (1) made progress last time out, finishing second at the end of 2200m at Bowraville. Drops back in trip and is among the chances. FLEE WITH ME (11) still chases the maiden but has efforts littered through his form good enough to threaten here. Keeping safe.
